data.title: Centerville, Indiana Population 2024
data.text:
Poverty in Centerville

The race most likely to be in poverty in Centerville is Black , with 52.63% below the poverty level.

The race least likely to be in poverty in Centerville is Multiple , with 5.83% below the poverty level.

The poverty rate among those that worked full-time for the past 12 months was 1.92% . Among those working part-time, it was 25.17% , and for those that did not work, the poverty rate was 22.33% .
